-- House Speaker Boehner to hold press conference
-- 
-- Mon Jul 25, 2011 2:08pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/07/25/us-usa-debt-boehner-idUSTRE76O4PF20110725

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - U.S. House of Representatives Speaker John Boehner has scheduled a press conference for 4 p.m. EDT Monday, his office said. 

 Boehner, the top U.S. Republican in Congress, is expected to discuss efforts to pass legislation raising the U.S. debt limit by an August 2 deadline. (Reporting by  Richard Cowan )